hat total, **~117 million MAUs** used Grok’s AI features.\n* **The Implied Percentage:** This means that approximately **21.3%** (117 million / 550 million) of the combined platform\'s monthly active users engaged with Grok\'s AI features.\n* **Tracking Methodology:** The filing notes that they track this specific subset of users "based on the source of their server requests" to differentiate between those who use Grok\'s AI features and those who do not. \n* *Note on the metric:* The 550 million MAU figure represents the *combined* unique users across both X and Grok (accounting for overlap so users aren\'t double-counted), rather than the X platform entirely in isolation.',
